title: Van Morrison 16 Bit Vinyl Pack
description:
Van Morisson - No Guru, No Method, No Teacher (original Holland pressing 830077-1)
Van Morrison - Astral Weeks (1975 US Burbank label WS 1768)
Van Morrison - Irish Heartbeat (original pressing MERH 124)
Van Morrison - Moondance (16604 Direct Disk Labs Half speed Master)
Van Morrison - Poetic Champion Compose (original Holland pressing 832585-1)
Van Morrison - Saint Dominic's Preview (1976 UK Burbank label K46172)
Van Morrison - Street Choir (Original UK pessing K 46066 Green Label)
Van Morrison - Tupelo Honey (original pressing UK K46114 Geen Label)

Cleaned with Knosti machine, LAT International fluid & ionised water.

Dedicated mains supply.

All contacts cleaned with Kontact & treated with Walker Audio Super Silver.

Linn LP12, Lingo, Ekos and Dynavector XX2 moving coil cartridge, LAT International IC 200 Mark II cables, Naim 62 pre-amp into Pioneer PDR-609 CDR, using TDK Audio Pro CD-R.

Declicked in reverse using iZotope RX2 Advanced.
